Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:35.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish I was there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:38.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:44.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度となにも失くさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:51.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私を忘れて　始めて　Restart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:55.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:24:00.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:05.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.75,0:24:09.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:12.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:14.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:16.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:20.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:22.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:23.81,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:57.06,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}請不要讓我離開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.31,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的觸碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.82,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不 請不要對生命無愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:07.19,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}儘管這絕望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:14.53,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}失準的時鐘 記錄著生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:18.54,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}散落滿地的記憶之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:22.33,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:27.46,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你看 卻是那麼輕易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:34.76,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消失殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:35.85,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我希望能與你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:38.06,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}請不要讓我離開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.06,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的觸碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:44.44,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}為了不再失去曾經擁有的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:51.45,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}讓我忘卻自己的過去 重新開始旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.66,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不 請不要對生命無愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:55.58,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}儘管這絕望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:24:00.21,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}願那讓你苦不堪言的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:05.54,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}會迎來完結的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.75,0:24:09.34,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而我卻要目送你離開
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:12.63,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們終將會重來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:14.76,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重來對新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:16.64,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:20.48,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們終將會重來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:22.56,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重來對新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:23.81,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}與你攜手邁進
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Title——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:55.06,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,650)\fsp5\c&HFFFFFF&}勇氣的{\c&HFDD595&}意{\c&HFFFFFF&}義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs+3\pos(1030,404)\c&HAD6B77&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6}D{\fs-3}mg{\r\c&H000000&\fn方正准圆_GBK\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6}:{\r\c&H000000&}        {\fn方正小标宋_GBK\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6}國\N\N\h\h\h\h\h{\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK}        {\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs-1}組
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6\c&H000000&\pos(1046,275)}動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6\c&H000000&\pos(1109,300)}漫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6\c&H000000&\fs-1\pos(1129,393)}字
